title: 2 Newark Police Officers Shot While Responding to 911 Call, Officials Say
description: Their injuries were not life threatening. The suspected shooter remained at large on Tuesday evening.
dc:creator: Liam Stack, Tracey Tully and Sarah Maslin Nir
media:credit: Bryan Anselm for The New York Times
media:description: The police taped off several blocks of Chancellor Avenue where the shooting occurred, and emergency vehicles swarmed the scene on Tuesday afternoon.
